#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.extract_kv.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.mf.extract_kv"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:1 of
msgid ""
"Extract values in key-value represented columns into standalone columns. "
"New column names will be the name of the key-value column followed by an "
"underscore and the key."
msgstr ""
"将键值对表示的列中的值提取到独立的列中。新列名将是键值列的名称后跟一个"
"下划线和键。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:5 of
msgid "The key-value columns to be extracted."
msgstr "要提取的键值对列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:7 of
msgid "Delimiter between key and value."
msgstr "键和值之间的分隔符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:9 of
msgid "Delimiter between key-value pairs."
msgstr "键值对之间的分隔符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:11 of
msgid "Type of value columns to generate."
msgstr "要生成的值列的类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:13 of
msgid "Default value for missing key-value pairs."
msgstr "缺失键值对的默认值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:15 of
msgid ""
"* If 'raise', then invalid parsing will raise an exception. * If "
"'ignore', then invalid parsing will return the input."
msgstr ""
"* 如果为 'raise'，则无效解析将引发异常。* 如果为 'ignore'，则无效解析将"
"返回输入。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:16 of
msgid "If 'raise', then invalid parsing will raise an exception."
msgstr "如果为 'raise'，则无效解析将引发异常。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:17 of
msgid "If 'ignore', then invalid parsing will return the input."
msgstr "如果为 'ignore'，则无效解析将返回输入。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:20 of
msgid "extracted data frame"
msgstr "提取的数据框"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.mf.collect_kv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:26 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.extract_kv.extract_kv:44 of
msgid ""
"The field names to be expanded are specified by columns kv_delim is to "
"delimit the key and value and '=' is default item_delim is to delimit the"
" Key-Value pairs, ',' is default The output field name is the original "
"field name connect with the key by \"_\" fill_value is used to fill "
"missing values, None is default"
msgstr ""
"要展开的字段名由列指定 kv_delim 用于分隔键和值，默认为 '=' item_delim "
"用于分隔键值对，默认为 ',' 输出字段名是原始字段名与键通过 \"_\" 连接 fill"
"_value 用于填充缺失值，默认为 None"

